e,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":301503,"user_name":"coder.js","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338120,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DE173A5D23690","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6b/08/15c473ef.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625721456,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5920688752","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"笔记<br><br>## 知识储备<br><br>任何新知识的理解，都要建立在旧的知识储备的基础上。你懂得越多，你学得越快。<br><br>学科与学科之间、科目与科目之间、知识与知识之间，并不是泾渭分明、毫无联系的。<br><br>学习和记忆的本质，就是把新知识与旧知识建立联系，你存储的旧知识越多，新知识学习起来就越快。<br><br>## 能力储备<br><br>如果有人看似不需要怎么努力，就可以做得很好。<br><br>那是人家一早在过去，在你看不到的时间里，就已经付出了足够的努力。<br><br>你的每一次练习，都会积累成你的本金。<br><br>这也就意味着，当你比别人晚四年开始努力时，即使你付出相等甚至双倍的时间，你可能也赶不上 TA 。<br><br>## 最后<br><br>种一棵树最好的时间是十年前，其次是现在。<br>","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":301502,"user_name":"coder.js","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338120,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DE173A5D23690","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6b/08/15c473ef.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625721023,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5920688319","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"所以说，“站在同一起跑线上”这句话，究竟骗了我们多少年。。。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":299599,"user_name":"Geek_gong1zu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2086659,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D629A6652AB8E2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1f/d7/03/db060811.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624757747,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5919725043","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"学习从来不是学习完全新的东西，而是将新东西与过去已学会的东西嫁接、联系，组合，因此你过去懂得东西越多，你就有更大的概率学会新的东西，并且新东西在你脑子里留下的印象更深。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":357087,"user_name":"Geek_67bed1","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1843567,"ip_address":"北京","ucode":"0186E90BA0437D","user_header":"http://thirdwx